Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! The stylish design elements of cinda b's Babe-A-Licious Baby Bag make it easy and oh-so-fashionable to tote all of baby's gear without sacrificing functionality. The hobo-style bag measures 15" wide x 6" deep x 12.5" inches high (not including the strap) and its features are many: a super-roomy interior with 4 slip pockets, a zippered cell phone pocket and a pen pocket. It also has 2 exterior side elastic slip pockets that are great for baby bottles, a comfortable adjustable crossbody strap and a secure magnetic snap closure. Oh, and because this beautiful bag is all about your beautiful little one, the Babe-A-Licious Baby Bag comes complete with cinda b's signature "easy open" changing pad. So, whether you're a new mom or trying to keep up with a toddler, cinda b beautifully takes you from the week to weekend outings without missing a beat! ABOUT CINDA B: After running a successful interior design business in Atlanta, Cinda found it difficult to find a fully functional, stylish bag that was versatile enough for the modern woman's everyday life. As a result, the cinda b brand was created. For cinda b, it's important to produce American handbags and create American jobs. Teaming up with one of the most experienced, well-known sewing companies in the country, each and every cinda b product is proudly made in the USA. Cinda b offers a variety of pattern options that combine bold and unique modern prints with effortless functionality.
